definitions.definition: The act of landing face first , as a result of an accident or error .
examples: The skater slipped off his board and did a painful faceplant .

definitions.definition: Death or defeat in a multiplayer online game .
A wrestling move in which an attacking wrestler forces an opponent down to the mat face-first without a headlock or facelock .

main_definition: ( informal ) The act of landing face first , as a result of an accident or error .
secondary_definitions: ( video games ) Death or defeat in a multiplayer online game .
( wrestling ) A wrestling move in which an attacking wrestler forces an opponent down to the mat face-first without a headlock or facelock .
